### ==============================
### PASARELA DE PAGOS
### ==============================

# Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Endpoint raíz
GET http://localhost:3000/
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Autorización interna del banco (existente)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/pagos/autorizar
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tarjcodigo": "1234567890123456",
  "monto": 100.50
}

###

# Procesar pago a través de la pasarela (nuevo)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/pagos/charge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": "MERCHANT_001",
  "amount": 150.75,
  "cardNumber": "1234567890123456",
  "expDate": "12/25",
  "cvv": "123"
}

###

# Procesar pago con datos inválidos (para probar validación)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/pagos/charge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": "",
  "amount": -10,
  "cardNumber": "123",
  "expDate": "invalid",
  "cvv": "12"
}

